ilk Mill|ja|富岡製糸場|qq=}} begins operations.
== Births == * {{ill|Keichō (era)|ja|Keichō|qq=}} 12 (Gregorian {{ill|1607|ja|1607th year|qq=}} {{ill|November 23|ja|11月23日|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Tokugawa Masako|ja|徳川和子|qq=}} (known as {{ill|Tōfukumon-in|ja|東福門院|qq=}} ), consort of {{ill|Emperor Go-Mizunoo|ja|後水尾天皇|qq=}} and daughter of {{ill|Tokugawa Hidetada|ja|徳川秀忠|qq=}} (+ {{ill|1678|ja|1678th year|qq=}} ). == Deaths ==
