nuelle/1872|qq=}} {{ill|November 4|ja|11月4日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/November 4|qq=}} ) – The government-run {{ill|Tomioka Silk Mill|ja|富岡製糸場|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tomioka Silk Mill|qq=}} begins operations.
